    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the \"reach out\" stuff doesn't really help when the person they'd be reaching out to doesn't even exist. it's just a script. i walk, i talk, i eat, but it feels like i'm just a ghost watching a movie of someone else's life. it's exhausting pretending to be real just to satisfy everyone else.",
